Rewrite the first equation as $\sqrt{2}\left(\sqrt{x y^{2}}-\sqrt{x^{2} y}\right)=6$ and let $\sqrt{x y^{2}}=u, \sqrt{x^{2} y}=v$, where $u \geq 0, v \geq 0$. Then the system in terms of $u$ and $v$ becomes

$$
\begin{aligned}
& \left\{\begin{array} { l } 
